Corresponding source
====================

The corresponding-source repository for Kit Pay for Android is:

    https://github.com/kitafrica33/kit-pay-android-source

Every distributed APK or Android App Bundle must have a public, annotated
`v<versionName>-code<versionCode>` tag in that repository matching the binary.
The tag and its release archives must contain the exact source used for the
binary, including build scripts, interface definitions, installation
information and Kit's modifications. A binary must not be distributed while
its corresponding tag or required source archives are inaccessible.

Release legal status
====================

This notice preserves evidence; it does not itself decide licence
compatibility. Internal distribution clearance
